{"id":23630,"date":"2024-02-21T14:34:49","date_gmt":"2021-07-21T09:04:49","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=23630"},"modified":"2024-11-12T17:47:38","modified_gmt":"2024-11-12T12:17:38","slug":"wardrobe-dimensions","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/wardrobe-dimensions\/","title":{"rendered":"What Are The Ideal Wardrobe Dimensions For Your Home?"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>A wardrobe can make or break the look of your home, so know about the wardrobe dimensions to get the best wardrobe for your home.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Wardrobes are an essential part of our <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">home\u2019s interiors<\/a>. An intelligently designed wardrobe provides ample storage space so you can keep your belongings in an organised way.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>It usually consists of three basic elements: Hanging closet, drawers and shelves to arrange your clothes, accessories, shoes, and other essentials in a clutter free manne.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>An efficiently designed wardrobe plays a key part in making your home look clean, organised and clutter free while the choice of material for finish adds to the overall aesthetics of your interiors. We bring to you all the details about wardrobe dimensions so you can design a tailor made one to fit your home, requirements, budget and preferences.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1424\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/04114833\/ideal-wardrobe-dimensions-for-your-home-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"Wardrobe dimensions (wardrobe width, wardrobe height and wardrobe depth) for your home\" class=\"wp-image-35750\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/04114833\/ideal-wardrobe-dimensions-for-your-home-scaled.jpg 1424w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/04114833\/ideal-wardrobe-dimensions-for-your-home-167x300.jpg 167w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/04114833\/ideal-wardrobe-dimensions-for-your-home-570x1024.jpg 570w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/04114833\/ideal-wardrobe-dimensions-for-your-home-768x1380.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/04114833\/ideal-wardrobe-dimensions-for-your-home-855x1536.jpg 855w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/04114833\/ideal-wardrobe-dimensions-for-your-home-1139x2048.jpg 1139w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/04114833\/ideal-wardrobe-dimensions-for-your-home-150x270.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1424px) 100vw, 1424px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Dimensions For A Swing Wardrobe<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Swing wardrobe or hinged wardrobe is one of the most popular <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/wardrobe-design\/\">wardrobe designs<\/a> in any home interior. They look elegant and are easy to organise. They usually have two front doors with hinges so make sure you have ample space in front of the wardrobe for a hassle free experience. You can also opt for a single shutter wardrobe depending upon the floor plan.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>The single shutter can start from <strong>two feet width<\/strong> with a standard <strong>height of seven feet<\/strong> and a <strong>depth of two feet<\/strong>.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>You can also accommodate a loft unit on top or opt for a floor-to-ceiling wardrobe as per your choice and convenience. Make sure the door panel is not more than <strong>60 centimeters<\/strong> or else it will create a lot of pressure on the hinges.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/21141234\/standard-wardrobe-dimensions-for-swing-wardrobe.jpg\" alt=\"Standard wardrobe dimensions for swing wardrobe with two front doors with hinges \" class=\"wp-image-23635\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/21141234\/standard-wardrobe-dimensions-for-swing-wardrobe.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/21141234\/standard-wardrobe-dimensions-for-swing-wardrobe-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/21141234\/standard-wardrobe-dimensions-for-swing-wardrobe-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/21141234\/standard-wardrobe-dimensions-for-swing-wardrobe-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Dimensions For A Sliding Wardrobe Dimension<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/sliding-wardrobe-design-ideas\/\">Sliding wardrobes<\/a> are space saving, convenient and trendy. Unlike hinged wardrobes they don&#8217;t need much space and are perfect for a small bedroom where the space between the bed and wardrobe is limited.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>The standard dimensions of a sliding wardrobe start from a <strong>width of six feet and can go upto 12 feet<\/strong> depending upon the floor plan, family size and requirements.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>The standard height and depth is constant at seven feet and two feet respectively.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Depending on the width you can choose two, three or even four sliders, for your wardrobe.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/21141255\/wardrobe-dimensions-for-sliding-wardrobe.jpg\" alt=\"Sliding wardrobe with space-saving dimensions and concealed hinges for a convenient, trendy design\" class=\"wp-image-23637\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/21141255\/wardrobe-dimensions-for-sliding-wardrobe.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/21141255\/wardrobe-dimensions-for-sliding-wardrobe-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/21141255\/wardrobe-dimensions-for-sliding-wardrobe-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/21141255\/wardrobe-dimensions-for-sliding-wardrobe-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Dimensions For A Walk-In Wardrobe<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Walk-In closets are fancy, luxurious and a dream corner in any home. But needless to mention it requires a big space and is quite tricky to accommodate in small apartments. Nevertheless if you are a proud owner of a spacious apartment or a villa then you have all liberty to gift your home with a lavish walk-in closet. The dimensions of your walk-in closet will depend upon your preferences Are you opting for a single sided, double sided or island walk in closets?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>The standard dimension is a minimum of <strong>seven feet by 10 feet<\/strong>.&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>A single side closet is about <strong>four to five feet deep<\/strong> and occupes <strong>24 inches of depth with 36 inches<\/strong> as clearance.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>A double sided closet can have two <strong>24 inches<\/strong> storage space on each side. It should have a <strong>36 inches<\/strong> space in the middle so the total width can come upto&nbsp; six to seven feet.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pro Tip<\/strong>: If you don&#8217;t have much space in your walk-in closet, try using a sliding door wardrobe, this will help you save space and make your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/walk-in-wardrobe-design-ideas\/\">walk-in wardrobe<\/a> look spacious.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/21141304\/wardrobe-dimensions-in-feet-for-walk-in-wardrobe.jpg\" alt=\"Walk-in wardrobe with dimensions in feet, showcasing a luxurious and stylish design.\" class=\"wp-image-23638\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/21141304\/wardrobe-dimensions-in-feet-for-walk-in-wardrobe.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/21141304\/wardrobe-dimensions-in-feet-for-walk-in-wardrobe-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/21141304\/wardrobe-dimensions-in-feet-for-walk-in-wardrobe-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/21141304\/wardrobe-dimensions-in-feet-for-walk-in-wardrobe-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Standard Dimension For Loft<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Loft is the extra space above the wardrobe that can be used as an excellent storage area to keep away all the items that are not required on a daily basis. Winter garments, blankets and other not so essential items can be stacked away from your line of sight during the summer season. A loft helps you access unreachable spaces in your home and gives a clean look. It helps save space in your wardrobe for your clothes, accessories and other necessary items.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>A standard loft has a<strong> width of six feet<\/strong> and <strong>depth of two feet<\/strong> for adequate storage.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/21141216\/standard-dimension-for-loft.jpg\" alt=\"Wardrobe size for loft above the wardrobe to keep all the items that are not required on a daily basis\" class=\"wp-image-23633\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/21141216\/standard-dimension-for-loft.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/21141216\/standard-dimension-for-loft-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/21141216\/standard-dimension-for-loft-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/21141216\/standard-dimension-for-loft-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, check out <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/loft-bedroom-ideas\/\">Loft Bedroom Design Ideas<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Standard Dimensions For Wardrobe Drawers<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A set of drawers in your wardrobe is essential for storage and easy access of your accessories, delicates and other essentials.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>So if you want to opt for multipurpose drawers then a <strong>depth of eight inches<\/strong> is ideal.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>For smaller drawer and to utilise space for bottom shelves and hanging area your drawers can be shallowers with a <strong>depth of four to six inches<\/strong>.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/21141226\/standard-dimensions-for-wardrobe-drawers.jpg\" alt=\"Standard dimensions for wardrobe drawers is essential for storage and easy access of your accessories, and delicates \" class=\"wp-image-23634\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/21141226\/standard-dimensions-for-wardrobe-drawers.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/21141226\/standard-dimensions-for-wardrobe-drawers-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/21141226\/standard-dimensions-for-wardrobe-drawers-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/21141226\/standard-dimensions-for-wardrobe-drawers-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Dimensions For Shoe Racks<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Adding a shoe rack to your wardrobe helps save space for separate shoe cabinets.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>A standard <strong>height of six to seven inches<\/strong> is good enough to house your shoes, sandals, high heels and sneakers.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/21141203\/dimensions-for-shoe-racks-in-wardrobe.jpg\" alt=\"Dimensions for shoe racks in your wardrobe is good enough to house your shoes, sandals, high heels and sneakers.\" class=\"wp-image-23632\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/21141203\/dimensions-for-shoe-racks-in-wardrobe.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/21141203\/dimensions-for-shoe-racks-in-wardrobe-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/21141203\/dimensions-for-shoe-racks-in-wardrobe-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/21141203\/dimensions-for-shoe-racks-in-wardrobe-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, check out <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/shoe-rack-design-ideas\/\">Shoe Rack Design Ideas<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can also customise it according to your needs if you have a collection of long boots or some designer gladiators.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe title=\"Things To Know Before Designing A Bedroom Wardrobe? | The Ultimate Guide On Wardrobes By DesignCafe\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/cN1zvwUwRdU?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope our detailed information about different wardrobe dimensions will help you design the best wardrobe for your home. If you are a little overwhelmed with so many technicalities we have end-to-end interior solutions for you. Our <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/\">interior designs<\/a> are tailor made to provide you with 20% more storage space and give you a clutter free living experience.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>With the best of materials, perfect finishes and hassle-free process DesignCafe will make your dream home come alive and in your budget.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>So book a consultation today and leave all the headache of dimensions and finishes on us. And for more such informative content about home interiors visit our blog and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/guides\/\">guide section<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you enjoyed reading about wardrobe dimensions, also explore <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/modern-wardrobe-designs-for-bedroom\/\">modern wardrobe designs<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Unwind In Your Person